why_filter: Some of the prefixes I've picked up might be seem rude or have multiple meanings, so I've put them as removed by default here. Feel free to add or remove. But yeah, Tit is a bird, Pimpleback is a mollusc, Crappie and Sucker are fish, etc.
note: Colours below don't map to coat colours directly, but rather are very literal and map to coat colours abstractly
